claim.claim-text:
A data processing apparatus comprising:
a first interface to which a device which reads data is connected;
a second interface to which a terminal apparatus is connected;
an identification information transmission unit for transmitting identification information to the terminal apparatus; and
a control unit for determining an association of the device and the terminal apparatus based on a correspondence of the read data and the identification information transmitted to the terminal apparatus when the data read by the device is input to the first interface.

A control method of a POS system comprising:
transmitting identification information from a data processing apparatus to a terminal apparatus;
receiving the transmitted identification information at the terminal apparatus and displaying the same on the terminal apparatus;
enabling a device to read the displayed identification information;
acquiring read data including the identification information which is read by the device, at the data processing apparatus, and
determining an association of the terminal apparatus and the device, based on the identification information included in the acquired read data.
